    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, sporting a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, creases, or fading. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the heated seats, operates exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented at authorized dealerships. It features a set of brand-new performance tires and has recently undergone a full inspection. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key collector-grade vehicle. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a clean vehicle history report.",
      "price": 48500.0,
