    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it truly looks like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like a dream and the interior is still smelling fresh. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
      "price": 44900.0,
