    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 that serves as a benchmark for the chassis. This example features the legendary S54 inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a whisper-quiet VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential with no fluid seepage. Crucially, the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with deep luster and zero panel gap irregularities. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters remain firm, free of the typical wear patterns seen in high-mileage units. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
